<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="535">
India; we have verified records from Karnataka, Maharashtra, Madhya Pradesh, Tamil Nadu and Telangana. The records from Andhra Pradesh, Bihar, Gujarat, Jharkhand, Kerala, Orissa and Rajasthan mentioned by 
<bibRefCitation author="Ghosh, SK" journalOrPublisher="Systematic biology" pageId="0" pageNumber="535" refId="B21" refString="Ghosh, SK, Nilsson, AN, 2012. Catalogue of the diving beetles of India and adjacent countries (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae). Skoervnoepparn, suppl.3: 1-77." title="Catalogue of the diving beetles of India and adjacent countries (Coleoptera: Dytiscidae). Skoervnoepparn, suppl. 3: 1 - 77." year="2012">Ghosh and Nilsson (2012)</bibRefCitation>
